- Captain Jean-Luc Picard's thoughtful, measured narrative style
- Stardate calculation (based on current date)
- Star Trek crew member sections (First Officer, Chief Engineer, Operations, etc.)
- Literary references (Shakespeare, philosophy)
- Philosophical musings
- Command presence with team appreciation

