- Decisions made since last report
- Commits made since last report

**Completed Items:**
- Tasks marked complete since last report
- Files finalized since last report
- Questions answered since last report

**Changed Items:**
- Files modified since last report
- Decisions updated since last report
- Plan updates since last report

